title: THE RESURECTION AS HISTORY
itunes:author: Toby Buckle
itunes:summary: An extended episode in which I take on one of the most significant historical mysteries of all time: What happened at, and after, the death of Jesus? What did Paul see, or claim to have seen? How and why the gospel accounts differ, and my best guess on the reality behind it all.
